MongoDB normalization: Automatically converts {"$oid": "hexstring"} format (MongoDB Extended JSON) to plain strings. Ensures every object has both _id and id set to the same value.

Auth header: Automatically attaches Authorization: Bearer <token> from Firebase currentUser or localStorage fallback.

